name: ExtensionSimpleRegisterMyCore
title: SimpleRegister (MY Core)
description: Extension used in appointment for simple registration without having to creating a patient resource.
purpose: Blood Bank Integration System (BBIS) v2 allows donor to book an appointment without having to register. To accomodate this integration requirement. MY Core created an extension for this purpose. This prevents creating a new patient resource for each booking as the registration is informal related to this particularly appointment only. Once patient arrived to the appointment they will be registered into the system formally..
